{"id": 2046, "genre": 1000, "title": "关于当代情感教育，你觉得哪些地方都跑偏了？", "description": "小兄弟，我这里有一本手到擒来神掌你要不要学一下？（题图来自：pixabay）", "record_count": 20012, "comment_count": 49, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171202141119ceBo5PrvRh8uydnZ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-12-10T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3365, "title": "关于当代情感教育，你觉得哪些地方都跑偏了？", "content": "关于当代情感教育，你觉得哪些地方都跑偏了？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 252946, "content": "青春期被要求抑制情感产生和表达，错过了最佳的时间", "image": "img/option/option/20171206234240Lu234WhvUwcKPMjq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252947, "content": "劝和不劝离的和事佬型忍让教育，“为了孩子”", "image": "img/option/option/20171206234255i23c6XPtRrNTGBQx.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252949, "content": "缺少系统科学的教育，多得是民间恋爱达人、约会学校", "image": "img/option/option/20171206235303AvUrOScDepR8s4xt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252951, "content": "恋爱秘籍化，强调技巧效率而非有关爱的知识思考", "image": "img/option/option/20171206235408L69tE8AFM7paqc4H.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252952, "content": "物化双方、看重条件交换的恋爱指南更像和亲指南", "image": "img/option/option/20171206235425wpUnejhq7RImvQO0.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252953, "content": "关于爱的语言，不教人自然表达，而教一些话术、金句", "image": "img/option/option/20171206235553ApUJFPg68tcyNlKG.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252955, "content": "不教人如何维系亲密关系，只教如何包装美化自己", "image": "img/option/option/20171206235608kvSNDAPf4xhbHKQl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252956, "content": "牵强附会，掰扯各种经济学理论，甚至干脆自造概念", "image": "img/option/option/2017120623562326mkJEO7aD0wKiYl.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}